important period of life

102
00:03:58,130 --> 00:04:01,210
because it resets our ability

103
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:04,290
to be focused, alert,
and emotionally stable

104
00:04:04,290 --> 00:04:06,240
in the wakeful period,

105
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:09,550
so we can't really talk
about wakefulness, focus,

106
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:12,610
motivation, mood, wellbeing

107
00:04:12,610 --> 00:04:14,160
without thinking about sleep,

108
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,180
and that's why we're
devoting this entire month

109
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:17,853
to the discussion about sleep.

110
00:04:17,853 --> 00:04:20,730
Now, we also can't talk about
